{"serial": "33026", "department_serial": 31, "code": "ME3054", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Electromagnetic and Electromechanical Machines", "ch": "電磁及電動機"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chen, Shih-Jui"], "ch": ["陳世叡"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["3", "4", "Z"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "220"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "機械工程學系", "en": "Department of Mechanical Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 13, "selected": 49, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "電磁及電動機為一門機電整合的課程，由同學熟知的電生磁、磁生電的觀念，來說明電機機械的基本運作原理，並進由這門科目讓同學能有以下的認知。\n1、法拉第電磁感應原理、安培右手定則及佛萊銘左手定則...等電磁基本理論。\n2、電動機的種類、結構及原理。\n3、發電機的種類、結構及原理。\n授課內容將結合理論與實際應用，讓修畢本課程的學生對電磁及電動機有更深一層的認識。", "en": "Learn the basic concepts of how electric motors work. Modelling and analysis of various types of generators and motors will be discussed. The course combines theory with practical applications so that students who complete this course can gain a deeper understanding of electromagnetism and electrical machinery."}, "outline": {"ch": "電機機械原理介紹\n變壓器\n交流電機基本原理\n同步發電機\n同步電動機\n各種其他發電原理", "en": "Electric Mechinery Introduction\nTransformer\nAC Generator\nAC Motor\nOther Energy Harvest Technique"}, "textbook": {"ch": "電機機械基本原理  5/e，Mc Graw Hill /東華書局Stephen J. Chapman 著，王順忠/陳秋麟 譯", "en": "Electric Mechinery Fundamentals 5/E, Stephen J. Chapman, McGraw-Hill"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "25", "en": "25"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n\n\n其他", "en": ["Lecture", "", "", "", "Others"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "平時分數：10%\n作業：15%\n期中考：35%\n期末考：40%", "en": "Participation/Attendance：10%\nHomework：15%\nMidterm exam：35%\nFinal exam：40%"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週二 1-3 pm", "en": "Tuesday 1-3 pm"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain"